For this project you will be needing the following libraries:-

<LiquidCrystal.h> https://downloads.arduino.cc/libraries/github.com/arduino-libraries/LiquidCrystal-1.0.7.zip
<Keypad.h> https://downloads.arduino.cc/libraries/github.com/Chris--A/Keypad-3.1.1.zip

How to add lib to the code
(Step-by-Step)

1. Go to these links and download the zip file
2. Open Arduino IDE software
3. Go to sketch and cick on Include Libraries
4. Then a explorer window will pop up on your screen
5. Select the Library LiquidCrystal Library
6. Then again go to the sketch, go to include lib
7. And this time select the Keypad Library.
8. Then copy paste the code (and if the include pop's up twice on the Arduino IDE then delete one part)

#Then Click Upload when you are done with the code.
